{"tid":135162,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"可能我只係等你親口拒絕我","createTime":"2017-02-26T06:53:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-06T10:44:04.000Z","uid":6251,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"78d4d9360ebe5c6e1723dbe4bfe3990ec2b5876e","tid":135162,"uid":6251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T06:53:04.000Z","msg":"我知道咁耐以黎可能都只係我一廂情願<br />\n可能你根本冇鍾意過我<br />\n甚至乎你連朋友都唔當係<br />\n但係我真係冇所謂<br />\n<br />\n我甚至會傻到成日去你屋企附近行黎行去，只係想撞下你，見下你，同你講幾句野就已經心滿意足。<br />\n<br />\n呢2晚好凍，我終於忍唔住whatsapp你，問你一句，我係你屋企附近，得唔得閒落黎見下面？<br />\n換黎嘅居然係已讀不回。<br />\n<br />\n我明知自己會衰，明知你冇當過我係咩，但你我唔介意，唔介意等，可能我等緊嘅唔係你應承我，而係等緊你一句拒絕我。"},{"pid":"5565a72caba8cdc07111e91a3d332d2d47d4918f","tid":135162,"uid":54576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T06:55:30.000Z","msg":"同佢住得好近？"},{"pid":"e7748c027dbe9010659c81dcf60a5b308ac31ffa","tid":135162,"uid":6786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T06:55:58.000Z","msg":"唔想做仆街咪唔親口拒絕你<br />\n做到咁明顯係人都知咩事啦<br />\n識做就自己走啦"},{"pid":"d66e9d03b7aa025638099f0882e7f4709baad26b","tid":135162,"uid":20725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T06:56:11.000Z","msg":"唔好再騷擾我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0efdf871b202c1e68c0e4bf5a8620a1601a03880","tid":135162,"uid":6251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T06:58:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔想做仆街咪唔親口拒絕你<br />\n做到咁明顯係人都知咩事啦<br />\n識做就自己走啦</blockquote><br />\n有邊個唔知發生咩事？有邊個唔知應該收皮？<br />\n大佬呀，放得低就放低左啦，洗唔洗你教呀"},{"pid":"ff36bceb3feac3d26fa5333256b63b6f4966abd9","tid":135162,"uid":6251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T06:59:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同佢住得好近？</blockquote><br />\n荃灣&gt;上環"},{"pid":"f4b50481041d59ac384dd1079506931422ed9784","tid":135162,"uid":61903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T07:03:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>同佢住得好近？</blockquote><br />\n荃灣&gt;上環</blockquote><br />\n痴漢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\ni know that feel"},{"pid":"c76d12394939b2a4fd285b3ed73114f48bcafea4","tid":135162,"uid":82940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T07:03:47.000Z","msg":"做男人咪咁垃圾"},{"pid":"b6675deb724e641d0b159a55753b524e8d9f0476","tid":135162,"uid":5700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T07:08:40.000Z","msg":"放手啦巴打，呢啲野大家心知肚明咪算"},{"pid":"5718f8243937e0dc46be822344a6c133eff3dfe0","tid":135162,"uid":33637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T07:09:55.000Z","msg":"不如你直接自爆啦<br />\n其實你明知個答案係點<br />\n只不過佢一日未拒絕 你都唔肯放棄啫<br />\n你話比佢聽你嘅感覺好過日怨夜怨啦<br />\n話知佢有咩反應 反正都唔關你事啦<br />\n可能你之後仲會掛住佢 都好過你以為自己仲有機"},{"pid":"5e1b9bbbff77b5867b4a7ed2bf0084497e328b09","tid":135162,"uid":34348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T07:10:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6374156a40bed9413c4c159c2be4ca7daafb8c78","tid":135162,"uid":36049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T07:20:31.000Z","msg":"比返小小男人既尊嚴自己啦"},{"pid":"1774557af4ec1a0e86322a82dd95d5792ce71bee","tid":135162,"uid":71008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T07:24:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e638eb0de9321e76ca0c2e4151b2032be14cb83","tid":135162,"uid":71008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T07:31:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />負皮"},{"pid":"c559ed12238c4740694fbff767c0b514f98a03a1","tid":135162,"uid":5234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T10:19:22.000Z","msg":"專登去到上環等咁on9，係我寧願去上環過大海博一博<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce836439278e0758b63eb0703dd1a8f5d21abded",